    "3b) in a so called 1 transistor 1 resistor (1T1R) structure, while the highest integration density would be achieved by a crossbar comprising no transistors, i.e., considering cells usually referred to as 1 resistor/ memristor (1R or 1M) structures or passive crossbar (Fig. 3c).",
